1. Molim te, *otvaraj* vrata (Please, open the door).
2. Nemoj da mi *otvaras* pisma (Don't open my letters).
3. Zbog ove klime moramo stalno da *otvaramo* prozor (Because of this air conditioning, we have to keep opening the window).
4. Nećeš verovati koliko se lakše diše kad se *otvori* prozor (You won't believe how much easier it is to breathe when you open the window).
5. *Otvori* kutiju i vidi šta se unutra nalazi (Open the box and see what's inside).
6. Moramo *otvoriti* novi račun u banci (We have to open a new account at the bank).
7. Kada *otvarate* novu firmu, morate paziti na mnoge stvari (When you open a new company, you have to be careful about many things).
8. Moja sestra će *otvoriti* svoju radnju uskoro (My sister will open her own store soon).
9. Svake godine gradonačelnik *otvara* manifestaciju (Every year the mayor opens the event).
10. Nemoj da mi *otvaraš* rane, molim te (Please, don't reopen my wounds).

(Note: The word "otvaraj" is in the imperative form in sentences 1, 5, and 10, in the present tense in sentences 2, 3, 4, and 10, and in the infinitive form in sentences 6, 7, 8, and 9.)